  "texts": [
    "By itself, such a free-form reconstruction is underdetermined and non-unique.",
    "To solve that problem, regularization can be applied, much as in the source reconstruction discussed above.",
    "Using a regularization, one can search, for instance, the smoothest model that fits the data, or the model the most similar to the light distribution.",
    "An early example of this technique in lensing is the reconstruction of Abell 370 by Abdelsalam et al. (1998).",
    "The mass map of Abell 2744 by Finney et al. (2018) is typical of more recent work on these lines."
  ],
